    This class makes it possible to pass parameters to modules.

    ModuleInvoker
    A class that calls Module.run(uniol.apt.module.ModuleInput, uniol.apt.module.ModuleOutput) according to specifications ModuleInputSpec and ModuleOutputSpec of a module.
